  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Hags interbreed with other races frequently, and those children who escape their grasp may pass their heritage on to later generations before it reemerges. The potent humors that accompany hag blood are better suited to a bloodrager’s ferocity than to traditional spellcasting.</em><br><br>Bonus Feats:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.pmAO1Sni8xx71pLF]{Blind-Fight}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.SUACufUXl12sUvnQ]{Deceitful}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.fVRnBIHR4Jq6btvm]{Great Fortitude}</li>\n<li>Improved Natural Attack,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.O0jbkTJcIji9BNiF]{Intimidating Prowess}</li>\n<li>Mother’s Gift.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Bonus Spells:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.to1cdmyh5rtfyg2s]{Chill Touch} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.k7cf5gshkp8xxqux]{Blindness/Deafness} (10th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.lsboosfk26m0ycqv]{Bestow Curse} (13th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.smbkd2yobhshbpqf]{Charm Monster} (16th)</li>\n</ul>"
